metadata.name: Spirit Rising (2004)
metadata.description:
This piece depicts the effort of humanity - or each of us individually - reaching outwards into the greater universe - overcoming the legacy that keeps out thinking on this sphere alone.

The figure is seen standing on a high peak surrounded by civilization. It's symbolic of how people often stand at as high a place as possible; gazing thoughtfully up into the heavens wishing to be able to journey further.

The winning collector will receive a personally signed print.

2777x2680
